MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2017-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 18th July, 2017
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 18th July, 2017:-
Shri M. Venkaiah Naidu relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Housing and
Urban Affairs; and the office of the Minister of Information and Broadcasting.
(i)
(ii)
Shri Narendra Singh Tomar assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Housing and
Urban Affairs. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Rural
Development; the office of the Minister of Panchayati Raj; and the office of the Minister of
Drinking Water and Sanitation.
(ii)
Smt. Smriti Zubin Irani assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Information and
Broadcasting. She will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Textiles.
(Bhaskar Dasgupta)
